WEBVTT

00:05.020 --> 00:06.854
Previously on Genius...

00:06.855 --> 00:08.356
Olga Khokhlova.

00:08.357 --> 00:09.857
Russian aristocracy.

00:09.858 --> 00:12.260
She must be looking for
the Duke or Viscount.

00:12.394 --> 00:13.895
I cannot let you in.

00:13.896 --> 00:15.229
We are not married.

00:15.230 --> 00:17.999
She certainly has
you under her spell.

00:18.033 --> 00:20.668
You're a married man,
with a reputation to protect.

00:20.669 --> 00:23.120
You spend your
days with your snob of

00:23.121 --> 00:26.744
a wife pretending you
are an aristocrat.

00:26.745 --> 00:29.443
At least I have not
abandoned my friends.

00:29.812 --> 00:32.613
I am the only Madam Picasso.

00:34.049 --> 00:35.550
Hey, Olga!

00:35.551 --> 00:37.885
Someday I'm going to
paint the perfect painting.

00:37.886 --> 00:39.420
I had no idea
you were so talented.

00:39.421 --> 00:41.723
Kahnweiler's been
asking me for new works to

00:41.724 --> 00:42.924
show, and I just...

00:42.925 --> 00:44.392
Don't have the time anymore...

00:44.393 --> 00:45.626
Go on.

00:45.627 --> 00:47.195
Play the game you played
the night we first met.

00:47.196 --> 00:48.997
Even when you missed,
you didn't flinch.

00:48.998 --> 00:51.099
She is so happy
when you are here, Pablo.

00:51.100 --> 00:54.503
Do you think Maya wants
to watch me cuddling Paloma?

00:54.603 --> 00:56.170
Maya loves Paloma.

00:56.171 --> 00:58.673
And how long do
you plan to keep me waiting?

00:58.674 --> 01:00.441
It did not occur
to me that you were interested

01:00.442 --> 01:01.609
in an old man.

01:01.610 --> 01:03.277
You don't seem old to me.

01:03.278 --> 01:04.779
Clear!

01:04.780 --> 01:06.447
I don't understand why
you let these women hang on.

01:06.448 --> 01:07.648
I should leave you.

01:07.649 --> 01:11.309
Ridiculous!
Nobody leaves Picasso!

